#### [NEW] `src/core/iam/dev-identity-provider.ts`

Creates a development/test operator identity for CAC (Credential Access Control). On startup via `start_web.bat`, this module:
- Generates a deterministic dev operator identity (`prism-dev-operator@localhost`)
- Creates a CAC-compatible session with unique session tokens
- Establishes per-tab session records in SQLite
- Emits `iam.session.created` events to the activity bus for full audit trail

